Company DescriptionGoldman, Sachs Management GP GmbH is  a Gesellschaft mit beschränkter Haftung registered in Germany with the Company reg no HRB78291 FRANKFURT AM MAIN. Its current trading status is "live". It was registered 2006-10-30.  The managing director is Laurie E. Schmidt,Michael Schramm.It can be contacted at  Friedrich-Ebert-Anlage 49, 60308 Frankfurt Am Main, Germany    .







 




